cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation and natural language processing. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural machine translation systems. Additionally, since the study involves professional translators, it could also be categorized under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with user perception and feedback.
